Game play is smooth and no lag which is always important. The aesthetics and graphics are appealing, and the characters are easy on the eyes to say the least. The story has an amusing and charming sass to it with an underlining seriousness to it with plenty of twists to keep you engrossed. There's character growth and replayability so you'll be coming back for more. Over all this is more than worth the price tag and it is one you'll never forget.
